# Proposal 
an 2D advanture game. the main character have to move around the map, killing enermy in sight, and
solving puzzles.

## Needs To Have
- map structure that allows the player to move around the map
- player must be able to attack, jump, and interact with its surrondings
- enemy and puzzle mechnism: hit box, interactives
- sound

## Nice To Have
- enemy ai
- animation for attacking and dying
- ending scene
- more map, enemy types, abilities, weapons, boss fight.etc
